<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        /* Internal CSS for privacy policy section */
        .privacy-policy-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .privacy-policy-box {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid purple; /* Set border color to purple */
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        /* Specific styling for the h1 tag */
        h1 {
            color: purple; /* Set text color of heading to purple */
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Specific styling for the p tag */
        p {
            color: darkpink; /* Set text color of paragraph to dark pink */
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Increase spacing between paragraphs */
            text-align: justify; /* Justify the text */
            padding: 0 20px; /* Add padding to the paragraph */
        }

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="privacy-policy-container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="privacy-policy-box" style="background-color: #f0f0f0;">
        <p>
            Stores, commonly known as supermarkets, food stores, and
            grocery stores, primarily engaged in the retail sale of all sorts of
            canned foods and dry goods, such as tea, coffee, spices, sugar, and flour; fresh fruits and vegetables; and fresh and prepared meats, fish, and poultry.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
